values: <font color="#ff0000" size="3">Fuck it all!!! For real!!! It's no longer worth it, it's not worth the pain, the tears, and the emotional ups and downs. I have 6 fucking days left of school and as of right now is concerned, I'm dropping it and you!</font>

It's been a while since I've updated. What can I say, my computer has been broken, lol.  
So whats new?....Not a whole lot....
               Prom was this weekend, it was pretty good but I must say it kinda put me in a bad mood :( It was at Paul Brown Stadium which was pretty cool. After we went to Angela's that was fun and Sunday we went to Crackle Barrel..MMMM so good. 
            People are still confuseing the hell out of me, More spaciffic a certin person. I thought I was good and I could move on, haha thats what I thought now the reality is, I have NO idea whats going on with that anymore. I still feel it, but I'm not sure whats happening on the other side. UGH why can't I just get the nerve to do something. UGH UGH UGH, I want it to all be ok, but for that to happen I'm going to have to get over being so shy and just say what I think.
            Only 2 more months till Graduation....I'm so excited....but so sad at the same time. I don't want to leave my friends and the people I love to death. Louisville or NKU, I'm not 100% sure yet, I guess well have to see what happenes in the next few weeks.
          WELL I can't really think of anything else thats going on, if you want some clarafication, just ask. Peace out!!
HAPPY BIRTHDAY TO ME !!!

So many emotions, So many tears.

Sitting by myself, thinking of you.

Wishsing that it wasn't true.

 

So my birthday is in SIX days, woop woop, right? Yeah, I'm thinking it's not going to be that way :( . Something tells me that it's going to suck. Come to think of it, the next few weeks are going to suck! I want school to be over, but what happens after that? Friends go their seperate ways, you loose the ones you love, you leave your family and the places you know best. I'm not ready for that!!! I don't know about anyone else, but I'm not ready.

There is still so many unanswered questions and so many mixed up emotions, and for me there still is a hole that needs to be mended, but if that is going to happen I am going to have to do something about it, cause i'm the only one that can. :(   :.(

So last night I sat in my basement by myself and watched Sweet Home Alabama and the Notebook. Prolly not the best thing to do since I have so many things going through my mind. Needless to say I cried. I also thought a lot about somethings, thats not good either.

Whats going on guys? I mean seriousley, why does everything happen the way it does and why do people act the way they do and how come nothing ever works out the way I want them to? It sucks.  And WHY IS THERE ABSOLUTLEY NOTHING TO DO IN NORTHERN KENTUCKY???

I need a guy, I need a date for Senior Dinner Dance, I need to save money, I need to do a lot of things. So why don't I have a guy? Why don't I have a date for Senior Dinner Dance? Why can't I save money?  If anyone can help me with my questions please feel free to let me know, k? Thanks.

On a brighter note...My Birthday is in 13 day's....Too bad it's prolly going to suck, and I'm not going to have or get what I really really want. Oh well, at least I'll get some money that I won't save. Whatever.

It's taking some time, but it's getting better. I have realized some things, and have delt with others. It's still hard to get rid of all thoes emotions cause everytime I see him, they come rushing back. I still have a long way to go but I'm getting there.

Things to do:

  • Study for Exams
  • Start/Finish art project Exam
  • Get more money
  • Save more money
  • Find another job
  • Find date for Senior Dinner Dance
  • Make plans for Spring Break
  • FIND ME A BOY!! (any suggestions?)
  • Deal with everything going on
  • Stop obsessing
  • Get over Justin! and Move on.

Damb I have a lot to do!!!

This Christmas I had Just one Wish,

My Christmas wish if you will,

A wished for you to be with me and to be sitting next to me,

Gift after gift,

Not this one but maby the next,

But as the last bow was undone and the last box opened,

You still were not with me and you hadn't called.

I sit here hopeing to find a box I over looked,

The box that is shoved in a corner waithing to be found,

The box that will bring me to you.

But I guess for now my Christmas wish will now be my New Years wish,

And if at the last stroke of 12,

My wish does not come true,

I will save it as my Birthday wish,

My birthday wish for you.

I will keep this wish as my only wish for however long it takes,

However long it takes to have you in my arms again.

<3

So the last few weeks have pretty much sucked...atleast when it comes to the guys.                                    

Tell me why is it so hard to give an explanation, thats all I want/need. It doesn't even have to be an in depth one, as long as I get one. Ugh!!! I have so many things going on and so many thing I have to worry about, I can't deal with it all. Maby after this semester is over some of the stress will go away, hopefully. Can't wait till Prom and Senior dinner dance, and all the Senior stuff in the spring, but I know that when they come, they will go so fast and then I will have to deal with leaving my friends and the places I know best, I don't want to think about that thought. I'm not really in the Christmas spirit at this point, mostly cause I have no one to share it with, and the one I want to share it with is being a fucking jackass, so thats not really helping me much either. I seriousley wish everything was perfect and the way i want them to be. Too bad thats not the case. I need a great night out where I am busy every second cause when I'm not doing something, I think, and when I get to thinking about whats going on, I get sad and I don't want to be sad, I just want to be happy. Is that too much to ask???  Ugh too much to think about..... Thanks to everyone who listens and is there for me to vent on, I really appreciate it, Love you all!!

It's amazing how everything can be super great one day, and the next, the one thing that means the most to you is gone, and everything is flipped upsides down.

Can't concentrate, can't stop thing about it, can't figure out why it happened, can't figure out how to get it back, and Can't understand why things always happenes to me!

Want to cry, but can't decide what to cry about

?????? I keep going over and over it in my head, and I still don't see why ??????

Ugh, not a good week and a half if you couldn't guess.

HAPPY THANKSGIVING!

So, today, I woke up, got ready went to my aunts for my mom's side of the family around noon. I LOVE my cousin Jessica and I don't really get to talk to her that much, so I talked to her for like two hours. Ate lots and lots of great homemade food, omg, my grandmas stuffing is sooo good! Played with my little cousins a little, then made my Christmas list for my god parents.

  Left aunts and went to grandma and grandpa's house for dad's side. Not too excieting. Ate ok food, grandma is crazy, so you know, haha. Pretty much only really talked to my brothers girlfriend, whatever, I love her, and she buys me cool stuff, haha

Came home, talked to Keri and Victoria. Somehow Victoria convinced me to go shopping with her tomorrow morning, yes black friday, and i'm hitting the mall at the crack of dawn. This is the second time this break that Victoria has gotten me up before 8.

Now I got to get some sleep so I can keep up with Victoria, hahaha, I love her though!!
Oh my god, I could not have asked to be any happier than I am right now. EVERYTHING is going great! I'm soooo happy, and so excited!!!

You were there to comfort me when I cried, so since you have already seen me cry, I guess I can let down that shield I'm holding up.

I will never be able to say all that is on my mind, I'm just not that type of person to say what I am thinking. I don't like saying what I'm feeling cause I'm affraid I'll hurt or lose someone that I care about. I know I shouldn't let what others do effect what I do, but it's so hard not to.  I just don't know what to do. I'm so out of it! I just wish everything was easier, like it was before, long before. I am very protective of the people I care about and I don't want them to make the wrong choices or do the wrong thing, but there is nothing I can do to change that. This isn't just friends, it's family too. My life is so confusing, I don't know what I want to do, I don't know where I belong, I don't know how I'm going to get through all this, I don't know what I will do if I lose someone very close to me, I have no idea what the hell I'm going to do for my art project, I don't know what I'm doing the rest of the weekend if anyhting, I don't know whats going to happen after my senior year, I don't know where I can go to be happy, I don't know who or what to believe, I don't know why I feel like this all the time, I don't know who people really are, I don't know who I can fully trust, I don't know who is telling me the truth, I don't know why I can't get the one thig I really want, and I don't know when all the madness is going to stop! I just don't know!  Ugh, I wish I was the person that could just go up so someone and tell them whats up, but I can't, I just can't do that. I can say that wasting 1/4 of gas just driving around by myself listining to the Postal Service didn't help to help me figure anything out, so I pretty much blew 1/4 tank of, like $10 that I paid for that 1/4 of a tank, and about an hour of my life. I need more than just an it's ok Kim, but I don't know what that is. 

I just wish I had an easy button!!!

Ok, so I'm going to be the first to admit it, yes, I did chicken out at the Hospital! The outside and that little hall way thig was enough for me, haha, so me and Keri sat it the car. I think that I scared myself more sitting in the car cause that town was creepy, no one around, creepy shadows in the windows, random sounds. I kinda regret not going in, but maby next time when the floors aren't covered with mud.  My favorite part was sleeping in the van, haha, I was so freakin cold though. If I rolled over too much, well, I'd be on the floor and I would have hit Keri in the head with my foot, sooo I couldn't move too much. So this was my day....

        12:00pm- woke up

        Sat around, took a shower, got ready

        Angela picked me, Christina, and Lindsey up.

        Taco Bell/KFC-mmm popcorn chicken

        Sat at Chris's house for a long while, funny pictures, seat belt haha

        Started to meet up with people

        Finally started the 45 min. journey to Maysville- hmm, N'Sync, Britney Spears what? crazy truck trying to rape us hahaha, it was going for you Angela, haha

       Got to the Hospital, chickened out, sat in the car w/Keri

       Took the 45 min. journey home, I drove Angela's car

        Kroger, pillow

  ~~ So, unless you were there, you can't fully know what went on, that will be a memory that I keep for a long time and when I'm 30 and married and have kids, I'll tell my parents and they won't be able to do anything about it, haha,  but OMG, it was so much fun, I love staying out all night, only next time I don't want to sleep in a car w/o a blanket.

THANK YOU!!! (you know who you are)

Hmmm, first day of school. It didn't feel like the first day, it felt like I had been there for months already. It's not like I had a hard day.

Foods- Listened to Mrs. Dawkins tell us how she doesn't eat pop tarts and how she almost burnt down her house when she put one in the toaster when she did eat them. Learned that she has a million pets, and found out what we were going to be cooking this semester.

Guidence Aid- haha sat in the guidence office with Marcus and Aundria and ate cake. haha I get to go to the teachers lounge and get drinks and you don't! haha.

English Lit.- Listened to Mrs. Mitsch talk about how we were seniors and howw we should know how to yet. She had yet to say "It's called be quiet", but it was only the first day. Oh how I hope I see her purple J-Lo jump suite this year, haha. We then made some sort of rubric thing about chocolate chip cookies, whatever.

2D/3D Art- Found out that it's pretty much Art 2 and 3 combines, both of which I have already taken, which means Mrs. Wilmhoff is going to let me do my own thing unless I want to do a project I have already done. Haha, yeah right, that really means I'll be doping a hole lot of nothing. Haha yes. But Allie is in that class only she is going to work on her AP stuff, but thats still going to be fun.

 

That's pretty much my day, I came home and took a nap, then ate dinner. 

Man, I wish it was May already and it's only been one day, 1 down 169 to go.

I'm feeling something, but I don't know what it is. I wish I knew cause then I could figure out how not to feel like that anymore. I do know that I'm very tense and I feel as though I am going to bust at any time. Wow I wish I knew how I felt, I wish , I wish I wish.

( I dorve the van, I love the van, I want to drive the van more, haha) We went to Victorias for a little bit after she got off work then all went down to the river to watch the boats go by. We then went home. Not the funnest but I laughed a lot.

There is one that I can go to when I need to release all of my worries and frustrations. They listen and it's weird cause we agree on a lot that I wouldn't think we would. I sometines think there not there for me, but in the end I know they will be. We discuss and come up with good solutions and laugh a lot!  (Thanks to them <3.)   I don't think you know who you are, and you will probably never see this, but it makes me feel better that it's out there.
